title: Flight Simulator 2020 - MSFS Update - World Update X USA - Lake Tahoe Airport
description:
In this video we will have a look at the handcrafted airport Lake Tahoe Airport (KTVL). The airport is located on the southern part of Lake Tahoe and  east from Sacramento and is surrounded by beautiful mountains. The airport is a good start it you want to visit one of the animal POI's which are part of MSFS.
